  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\">\n<p><strong>Want to keep learning?  </strong></p>\n<p>Our <a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/courses/learn-kansaiben-online\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Kansai-ben course</strong></a> is perfect for those who want to learn about the differences between standard Japanese and the Kansai regional dialect, and our <a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/manage/courses/741924/settings\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>PEKO-PEKO </strong></a>course teaches all about Japanese Onmatopiea to help improve your conversational fluency.</p>\n<p>We also regularly add new courses and content to our platform, check out our latest courses<strong> <a href=\"\">here</a>.  </strong></p>\n<p><strong>Want to keep access to the course material?</strong></p>\n<p>You have access to the course and community for six months from the date you signed up, however, if you want to keep access for longer you can sign up for our subscription option. Only available to Akamonkai Japanese 12-week beginner course alumni, it allows you to access the content and community for as long as you would like through a monthly subscription charge.</p>\n<p>This offer is only available for people who have previously signed up to the 12-week Akamonkai Beginner course, and right now there is<strong> a special introduction price of only 500¥ for the first month!</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/bundles/akamonkai-alumni-subscription\">SUBSCRIBE HERE</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Want more study advice?</strong></p>\n<p>There is a whole section on the Go! Go! Nihon Blog devoted to Japanese lessons, study tips and more, you can find it<strong> <a href=\"https://gogonihon.com/en/blog/category/learn-japanese/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">here.</a> </strong></p>\n<p><strong>Have questions about living and studying in Japan?</strong></p>\n<p>We've helped over 7000 students achieve their dream of coming to Japan to live and Study, so if you have any questions about how we could help you, please don't hesitate to get in touch!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://gogonihon.com/en/#ContactForm\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/cff/f52/f95/Contact_us.png\" style=\"width: 168px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" srcset=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/cff/f52/f95/Contact_us.png?width=1920 1x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/cff/f52/f95/Contact_us.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=2 2x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/cff/f52/f95/Contact_us.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=3 3x\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>And don't forget to follow Go! Go! Nihon online:</strong></p>\n<table class=\"fr-dashed-borders\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 20.0738%; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/GoGoNihonGo\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/870/625/991/Icon_youtube.png\" style=\"width: 55px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" srcset=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/870/625/991/Icon_youtube.png?width=1920 1x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/870/625/991/Icon_youtube.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=2 2x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/870/625/991/Icon_youtube.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=3 3x\"></a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 20.0738%; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/gogonihon/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/179/ed3/2b4/Icon_Instagram.png\" style=\"width: 55px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" srcset=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/179/ed3/2b4/Icon_Instagram.png?width=1920 1x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/179/ed3/2b4/Icon_Instagram.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=2 2x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/179/ed3/2b4/Icon_Instagram.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=3 3x\"></a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 19.9262%; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/gogonihon\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/90a/481/618/Icon_twitter.png\" style=\"width: 58px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" srcset=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/90a/481/618/Icon_twitter.png?width=1920 1x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/90a/481/618/Icon_twitter.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=2 2x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/90a/481/618/Icon_twitter.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=3 3x\"></a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 19.9262%; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/learn.Japanese.study.Japan\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/bf8/091/d76/Icon_facebook.png\" style=\"width: 56px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" srcset=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/bf8/091/d76/Icon_facebook.png?width=1920 1x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/bf8/091/d76/Icon_facebook.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=2 2x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/bf8/091/d76/Icon_facebook.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=3 3x\"></a></td>\n<td style=\"width: 19.9262%; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://vm.tiktok.com/7q6rTK/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/506/87b/5a0/Icon_tiktok.png\" style=\"width: 54px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" srcset=\"https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/506/87b/5a0/Icon_tiktok.png?width=1920 1x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/506/87b/5a0/Icon_tiktok.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=2 2x, https://files.cdn.thinkific.com/file_uploads/259518/images/506/87b/5a0/Icon_tiktok.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=3 3x\"></a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</div>",
